        <a href="http://people.ubuntu.com/~ubuntu-security/cve/CVE-2013-1676">CVE-2013-1676</a>, 

        <a href="http://people.ubuntu.com/~ubuntu-security/cve/CVE-2013-1677">CVE-2013-1677</a>, 

        <a href="http://people.ubuntu.com/~ubuntu-security/cve/CVE-2013-1678">CVE-2013-1678</a>, 

        <a href="http://people.ubuntu.com/~ubuntu-security/cve/CVE-2013-1679">CVE-2013-1679</a>, 

